{"type": "article", "id": 22320, "title": "毒菌家具系列", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-16T07:30:14Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 29, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702115133o5ah3TLWnNQgmDIy.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>这套家具名为 toadstool（毒菌），包括沙发、座位和边桌。桌面和座位面是绿色、蓝色、红色和粉色的软垫，搭配在一起有种孟菲斯的风格，造型可爱而颜色鲜艳。彩色绒垫下的支撑使用了木材、金属或大理石，有了不同材料的冲击，增加了趣味性。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115131cd6ejwvfmXSBTy5k.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021151320kgEHLJFeZrzCw9Q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.01589242\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115132ysutBjVTCXmroqYZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.79462103\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure><br></figure>\n\n"}